Preface

title: 1  Introduction
text:
This is a book created from markdown and executable code.
See Knuth (1984) for additional discussion of literate programming.




Knuth, Donald E. 1984. “Literate Programming.” Comput. J. 27 (2): 97–111. https://doi.org/10.1093/comjnl/27.2.97.

title: 2  Summary
text: This book will cover data science concepts. This will contain longer form content from the ds_skills repository

title: 3  Optimization
text: Optimization is the study of finding the best output from the best combination of inputs.
